Package com.espertech.esperio.jms

Interface Summary
JMSMessageMarshaller Interface for a marshaller that creates a JMS message given a JMS session and event.
JMSMessageUnmarshaller Interface for a un-marshaller that takes a JMS message and creates or wraps an event object for use to send as an event into an engine instance.
 

Class Summary
JMSDefaultAnyMessageUnmarshaller Created for ESPER.
JMSDefaultMapMessageMarshaller Marshals the response out of the event bean into a jms map message.
JMSFixProtocolTextMessageMarshaller Marshals the response out of the event bean into a jms map message.
JMSFixProtocolTextMessageUnmarshaller Unmarshaller for FIX protocol messages.
JMSInputAdapter Created for ESPER.
JMSOutputAdapter Implements a JMS output adapter.
JMSSubscription Represents the JMS-aspects of a subscription.
SpringJMSTemplateInputAdapter Input adapter for receiving engine from the JMS world using Spring JMS templates and sending these to an engine.
SpringJMSTemplateOutputAdapter Output adapter for sending engine events out into the JMS world using Spring JMS templates.
